1
00:00:13,820 --> 00:00:15,740
♪Showing my weakness is a facade♪

2
00:00:15,740 --> 00:00:17,540
♪The aim is to lure you into the trap♪

3
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:19,140
♪You can only see clearly♪

4
00:00:19,140 --> 00:00:21,300
♪If you sacrifice all your naivety♪

5
00:00:21,300 --> 00:00:23,380
♪This hunting game♪

6
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:25,180
♪Trust is doubtful♪

7
00:00:25,180 --> 00:00:28,780
♪Seducing is also a kind of trick♪

8
00:00:28,780 --> 00:00:31,540
♪Who is still fantasizing♪

9
00:00:31,540 --> 00:00:32,860
♪Longing and hoping for a miracle?♪

10
00:00:32,860 --> 00:00:35,100
♪Who has eyes♪

11
00:00:35,100 --> 00:00:36,700
♪Filled with helplessness,
despair and devoid of light?♪

12
00:00:36,700 --> 00:00:38,780
♪Who is still waiting♪

13
00:00:38,780 --> 00:00:40,340
♪For the broken soul to be warmed?♪

14
00:00:40,340 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Who finally chooses to move forward?♪

15
00:00:45,780 --> 00:00:49,620
♪I will crush and trample every danger♪

16
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,740
♪Strategising step by step.
Taking initiative to begin the game♪

17
00:00:53,740 --> 00:00:57,500
♪Taking control of the game.
Love should not be compromised♪

18
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:00,780
♪Disguise is just an opening song♪

19
00:01:00,780 --> 00:01:03,460
♪I will be patient and cautious♪

20
00:01:03,460 --> 00:01:05,180
♪Controlling the end in the shadows♪

21
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:07,100
♪You are unexpected♪

22
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,660
♪The biggest surprise
given to me by God♪

23
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:14,100
♪Let's welcome the dawn
after a dark night together♪

24
00:01:14,500 --> 00:01:17,580
♪Before embracing each other
and breaking out of this with love♪

25
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:21,880
=Her Disguise=
(Adapted from Shuiyue Xianling's novel, "Her Disguise")

26
00:01:22,140 --> 00:01:24,860
=Episode 16=

27
00:01:25,319 --> 00:01:26,719
I was there when father died.

28
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,040
There was no note.

29
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,200
Father didn't want to hurt you,

30
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,840
so he kept it from you.

31
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:36,079
This last letter

32
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:38,560
was witnessed and signed

33
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:39,680
by Mr. Zhou.

34
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:40,780
If you don't believe it,

35
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,920
submit it to the court.

36
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:46,120
Haoran, it's true.

37
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:50,560
Uncle asked me to find a lawyer

38
00:01:50,760 --> 00:01:52,079
before he died.

39
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,280
We just didn't tell you.

40
00:01:56,719 --> 00:01:58,159
That's quite a trick.

41
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:02,640
Write it down.

42
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:04,519
Haoran.

43
00:02:05,079 --> 00:02:06,719
The Lu family is in crisis.

44
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,479
Leaving would give

45
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:10,280
everyone a chance

46
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,960
and clear the family's name.

47
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,360
After all these years,

48
00:02:15,360 --> 00:02:16,520
I hope you can show

49
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:18,560
this last bit of loyalty.

50
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:22,719
Second Young Master Lu, look here.

51
00:02:32,360 --> 00:02:34,240
Second Young Master Lu, this is true.

52
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,439
You should return

53
00:02:36,700 --> 00:02:37,759
all the Lu family's assets.

54
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:52,000
Your idea?

55
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,000
Also,

56
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:07,400
I'd like to announce

57
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,280
that on the 15th of next month,

58
00:03:10,120 --> 00:03:11,719
I will be marrying

59
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,240
Miss Lin Mange.

60
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:28,759
Xiang.

61
00:03:30,599 --> 00:03:32,599
Transform this room into a bridal suite.

62
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,479
Replace all the bed linens and curtains

63
00:03:34,680 --> 00:03:35,680
with new ones.

64
00:03:35,919 --> 00:03:36,840
Yes, Eldest Young Master.

65
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,120
Haoran.

66
00:03:45,719 --> 00:03:46,400
Let's go together.

67
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:50,759
Some people aim high.

68
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:54,759
But we know what's right and wrong.

69
00:03:54,889 --> 00:03:56,458
♪Trust is doubtful♪

70
00:03:56,479 --> 00:03:57,479
I've made up my mind.

71
00:03:57,498 --> 00:04:00,041
♪Seducing is also a kind of trick♪

72
00:04:00,560 --> 00:04:01,360
I'm staying.

73
00:04:01,408 --> 00:04:02,710
♪Who is still fantasizing♪

74
00:04:02,720 --> 00:04:04,038
♪Longing and hoping for a miracle?♪

75
00:04:04,041 --> 00:04:05,803
♪Who has eyes♪

76
00:04:05,803 --> 00:04:07,602
Though I'm not a biological son,

77
00:04:08,080 --> 00:04:10,120
father entrusted me on his deathbed

78
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,800
to take care of the family

79
00:04:12,319 --> 00:04:13,639
and be responsible for it.

80
00:04:14,639 --> 00:04:16,000
Since Guanghe is getting married,

81
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:17,279
as his younger brother,

82
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,240
I must do my part.

83
00:04:19,301 --> 00:04:21,219
♪I will crush and trample every danger♪

84
00:04:21,600 --> 00:04:22,279
Fine.

85
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,120
You may stay.

86
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:27,040
But you'll only be a servant.

87
00:04:27,064 --> 00:04:28,739
♪Love should not be compromised♪

88
00:04:28,787 --> 00:04:31,655
♪Disguise is just an opening song♪

89
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,519
Did you hear that?

90
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,759
Xiang.

91
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:35,560
Give him the servant's clothes.

92
00:04:36,421 --> 00:04:38,235
♪You are unexpected♪

93
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:38,959
Second Young Master.

94
00:04:39,480 --> 00:04:41,600
These are my clothes, just washed.

95
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:44,360
I hope you don't mind.

96
00:04:45,456 --> 00:04:47,309
♪Before embracing each other
and breaking out of this with love♪

97
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:47,920
You...

98
00:05:01,120 --> 00:05:02,720
The criminals were captured,

99
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:05,160
and the map was given
to the military intact.

100
00:05:07,399 --> 00:05:08,720
The marshal praised you, Mange,

101
00:05:09,260 --> 00:05:10,360
for your great contribution.

102
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:15,680
But I gave the map out.

103
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,040
Shouldn't I be guilty?

104
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:18,639
How could that be?

105
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:21,079
You preserved the map

106
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:23,839
and hid key information,

107
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,800
so you've earned praise.

108
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,439
Remembering that final detail

109
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:33,240
would make your contribution
even greater.

110
00:05:38,839 --> 00:05:41,560
I saw it from one of my patients,

111
00:05:42,839 --> 00:05:44,120
but it was too long ago.

112
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,240
I can't remember

113
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,399
which patient.

114
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:48,360
Guanghe.

115
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:49,680
Let me think about it.

116
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,480
I could

117
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,560
make a fake map,

118
00:06:01,879 --> 00:06:04,480
but the thought of others faking it
pains me,

119
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:06,720
so I end up drawing the real one.

120
00:06:09,319 --> 00:06:10,040
Guanghe.

121
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,519
With this map,

122
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,040
will the Lu family's business

123
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,439
run smoothly?

124
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:15,920
Of course.

125
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:18,279
Mr. Qin and the marshal are old friends.

126
00:06:19,079 --> 00:06:20,720
As the Chamber of Commerce president,

127
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,600
Mr. Qin will naturally look after
the Lu family's business.

128
00:06:30,600 --> 00:06:31,399
Eldest Young Master,

129
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:34,199
having a virtuous wife
like Young Madam

130
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,959
is truly an honor for the Lu family.

131
00:07:05,639 --> 00:07:07,600
Did you find what you were looking for?

132
00:07:11,399 --> 00:07:12,079
Second Young Master.

133
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,290
Eldest Young Master asked us
to tidy up the room.

134
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:16,399
Moving you to the attic storage,

135
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:19,680
and this room will be
Young Mistress Lu's studio.

136
00:07:41,309 --> 00:07:46,647
♪The sun shines blindly on us♪

137
00:07:48,431 --> 00:07:53,760
♪Locking away a new future♪

138
00:07:54,652 --> 00:08:01,027
♪No more progress,
gradually becoming numb♪

139
00:08:01,912 --> 00:08:08,232
♪I start to believe
that this is my destiny♪

140
00:08:09,747 --> 00:08:15,311
♪Your sudden appearance
has turned the world upside down♪

141
00:08:15,319 --> 00:08:16,439
There's just one corner left.

142
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:17,720
We can finish it next time.

143
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:19,000
It's been too long.

144
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:20,160
I'm worried it's too much for you.

145
00:08:22,516 --> 00:08:26,043
♪If the answer is hidden
in a perfect puzzle♪

146
00:08:26,047 --> 00:08:26,727
Lin Mange.

147
00:08:30,150 --> 00:08:33,023
♪Can you find your way back?♪

148
00:08:33,039 --> 00:08:33,759
Lin Mange.

149
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,639
Are you doing this on purpose?

150
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:45,879
Young Madam Lu.

151
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,679
My map became your stepping stone.

152
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:56,919
Shouldn't you thank me?

153
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,080
Don't forget, there's still one corner

154
00:09:05,039 --> 00:09:05,679
left to finish.

155
00:09:06,759 --> 00:09:09,320
You still have many friends
in the orphanage.

156
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:16,960
Guanghe.

157
00:09:17,690 --> 00:09:18,799
I'll help with the moxibustion.

158
00:09:22,200 --> 00:09:25,679
A servant should have some sense.

159
00:09:26,450 --> 00:09:27,559
Why aren't you coming to help?

160
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:47,000
Does it hurt?

161
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:49,039
It doesn't hurt.

162
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,919
How can I be in pain

163
00:09:51,640 --> 00:09:52,850
when you're so good at what you do?

164
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,320
Hold on a bit.

165
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:59,639
If it hurts, just hold my hand.

166
00:10:04,960 --> 00:10:05,559
Give it to me.

167
00:10:16,639 --> 00:10:17,720
Sorry, Eldest Young Master.

168
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,600
Never done servant work before?

169
00:10:20,559 --> 00:10:21,240
Sorry about that.

170
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,120
Don't know how?

171
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:25,720
You can learn.

172
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,440
Start with the basics.

173
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,919
Clear the dead branches in the yard.

174
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,960
If you don't finish,

175
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,559
don't sleep tonight.

176
00:11:00,879 --> 00:11:01,639
Lin Mange.

177
00:11:03,260 --> 00:11:04,399
Are you doing this on purpose?

178
00:11:47,639 --> 00:11:50,799
(Next time, I want it all.)

179
00:11:55,830 --> 00:11:58,870
♪Bye, weakness♪

180
00:11:59,790 --> 00:12:07,790
♪Missed opportunities sink
into the ocean with the setting sun♪

181
00:12:08,830 --> 00:12:14,670
♪Butterfly leaves the land of taboo♪

182
00:12:15,550 --> 00:12:19,950
♪The rotten mud rots away the malice♪

183
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:28,710
♪The fallen
naively wipes away the color♪

184
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:35,910
♪The soul wakes up
in the dangerous forest♪

185
00:12:37,310 --> 00:12:43,110
♪Crushing the mundane
and ever changing mask step by step♪

186
00:12:43,110 --> 00:12:48,590
♪The crow stops whispering in the fog♪

187
00:12:49,550 --> 00:12:57,390
♪Black rose blooms
at the end of the abyss♪

188
00:12:57,390 --> 00:13:03,190
♪It is a beautiful scar on my wound♪

189
00:13:03,750 --> 00:13:06,670
♪Overcoming hardships♪

190
00:13:06,670 --> 00:13:12,990
♪A strong armor
wards off criticisms and disputes♪

191
00:13:13,630 --> 00:13:17,550
♪My brilliant life♪

192
00:13:18,110 --> 00:13:22,070
♪No matter who says anything♪

193
00:13:22,070 --> 00:13:25,750
♪I won't be hurt anymore♪

194
00:13:25,750 --> 00:13:32,070
♪If kindness goes away,
I'd rather be sharp♪
